‘Street Voice’ on TV Independent asked Nigerians one simple question as the country celebrates 59 years of Independence from colonialism: “What are your thoughts about Nigeria at 59?” What do you think of Nigeria as it celebrates this 59th anniversary? Please leave your thoughts in the comment below. —
